    "name": "Stellarcraft",
    "steam_appid": 3189820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/71b177df523528f2a0b3b21ff96fccf7.poster.avif?t=1772345696\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/71b177df523528f2a0b3b21ff96fccf7.webm?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/71b177df523528f2a0b3b21ff96fccf7.mp4?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stellarcraft</strong> is a <strong>sci-fi tower defense game</strong> where you explore different planets, gather resources, and complete missions. Build and upgrade defensive structures to fend off enemy waves and develop your character. <strong>Strategic planning and technological upgrades are the key to success.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>solo or in co-op mode with up to 4 players</strong> and face the challenges of the universe together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/a119d2358d249e9eaf7efec10598deb4.avif?t=1772345696\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras_big/a119d2358d249e9eaf7efec10598deb4.avif?t=1772345696 width=800 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/b6f2357558383b1f4443ef57d9ffb994.poster.avif?t=1772345696\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/b6f2357558383b1f4443ef57d9ffb994.webm?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/b6f2357558383b1f4443ef57d9ffb994.mp4?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different planets with unique biomes and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each planet offers different resources and enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your exploration to find strategic positions for your defenses. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/a119d2358d249e9eaf7efec10598deb4.avif?t=1772345696\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras_big/a119d2358d249e9eaf7efec10598deb4.avif?t=1772345696 width=800 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/830817ea12b30497bb26da89c8ee93ed.poster.avif?t=1772345696\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/830817ea12b30497bb26da89c8ee93ed.webm?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/830817ea12b30497bb26da89c8ee93ed.mp4?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources such as minerals, energy and rare metals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resources are crucial for building and upgrading defenses. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Certain planets have special resources that are needed to produce advanced technology. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/a119d2358d249e9eaf7efec10598deb4.avif?t=1772345696\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras_big/a119d2358d249e9eaf7efec10598deb4.avif?t=1772345696 width=800 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/825d4bffb4e89a4c39b819e81fa8accc.poster.avif?t=1772345696\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/825d4bffb4e89a4c39b819e81fa8accc.webm?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/825d4bffb4e89a4c39b819e81fa8accc.mp4?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build different towers and defenses to defend yourself against waves of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each tower has unique abilities and upgrades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place your defenses strategically to maximize efficiency and conserve resources. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/b154bc5cf16357cb8854c75bbd5ff8d5.poster.avif?t=1772345696\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/b154bc5cf16357cb8854c75bbd5ff8d5.webm?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189820/extras/b154bc5cf16357cb8854c75bbd5ff8d5.mp4?t=1772345696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your turrets by crafting enhancements and equipping them to your turret.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This grants them shields, more ammunition, or extra abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
